---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import {
  BookOpen,
  Compass,
  Award,
  Lightbulb,
  GraduationCap,
  ArrowRight,
} from "@lucide/astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us - ScholrBee">
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <Header />

  <div class="px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-50 flex flex-col">
    <!-- Intro Header Section -->
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-20 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <span
        class="text-label-md text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.12em] mb-3"
        >Our Mission</span
      >
      <h1 class="text-headline-xl text-primary max-w-3xl leading-tight">
        Elevating Scholarly Focus Through Mindful AI
      </h1>
      <p
        class="mt-6 text-body-md sm:text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed"
      >
        ScholrBee was founded on a simple realization: the modern researcher is
        overwhelmed by information but starved for synthesis. We build tools
        that reduce cognitive load, so you can focus on making meaningful
        connections.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Pillars Grid -->
    <section class="py-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div
        class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/40 rounded-[24px] p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-subtle hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-700 mb-6"
        >
          <GraduationCap class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">
          Academic Excellence
        </h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Crafted with advice from top scholars and learning scientists. We
          construct learning experiences around active recall, spaced
          repetition, and visual linking.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/40 rounded-[24px] p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-subtle hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 mb-6"
        >
          <Lightbulb class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">
          Intuitive Synthesis
        </h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          AI shouldn't do the thinking for you. Our system acts as an amplifier,
          highlighting key details and suggesting organic links without
          overriding your voice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/40 rounded-[24px] p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-subtle hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 rounded-2xl bg-rose-50 flex items-center justify-center text-rose-700 mb-6"
        >
          <Compass class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">
          Mindful Technology
        </h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          We reject the attention economy. ScholrBee has a beautifully quiet
          aesthetic, promoting focus over distraction and deep research over
          constant notifications.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Detailed Narrative & Visual Callout -->
    <section
      class="py-12 sm:py-20 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center"
    >
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-headline-lg text-primary">The ScholrBee Story</h2>
        <p
          class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-justify"
        >
          It began in research libraries and late-night study lounges. We
          noticed that while students and professional researchers had more
          access to papers than ever, the cognitive load of organizing notes,
          matching patterns across sources, and reviewing complex concepts was
          pulling them away from actual creative thinking.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-justify"
        >
          We realized that a folder of PDFs is a graveyard of ideas. We wanted
          to build a "Second Brain" that isn't just a cabinet, but an active
          discussion partner.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-justify"
        >
          In 2025, we assembled a team of learning designers and software
          engineers to build ScholrBee. Since then, thousands of students,
          researchers, and professional thinkers have elevated their academic
          potential with our academic-chic workspace.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex-1 bg-[#012d1d] text-[#ffdea9] rounded-[28px] p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-lg flex flex-col justify-between h-full min-h-[320px]"
      >
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-on-primary-container"
            >Our Promise</span
          >
          <h3
            class="font-display text-headline-lg text-white mt-4 leading-tight"
          >
            We are committed to helping you study smarter, not busier.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-body-md mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            We promise to keep your notes private, your interface focused, and
            our features grounded in proven research principles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="/app"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#ffdea9] text-[#271900] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white transition duration-300"
          >
            Join the Hive <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="py-12 border-t border-b border-outline-variant/30 my-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <span class="block font-display text-[44px] font-bold text-primary"
            >150k+</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary"
            >Notes Connected</span
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block font-display text-[44px] font-bold text-primary"
            >98%</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary"
            >Satisfaction Rate</span
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block font-display text-[44px] font-bold text-primary"
            >2.5x</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary"
            >Faster Learning</span
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block font-display text-[44px] font-bold text-primary"
            >45+</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary"
            >Countries Reached</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
